variables.description:
JSON mapping public model aliases (keys) to internal model_name values (values). Used by /v1/models and /v1/chat/completions.

Example:
{
  "flash": "deepseek-v4-flash",
  "pro": "deepseek-v4-pro"
}

JSON mapping model aliases to base system prompts. The base prompt is always injected as the first system message — the user cannot override it. If the request also includes a system message, it is appended after the base prompt.

Example:
{
  "flash": "You are a fast, concise assistant. Keep responses brief and direct.",
  "pro": "You are a thorough, analytical assistant. Provide detailed reasoning."
}
